sentences.english: I'm at my wits end worrying about how to pay the bill.
sentences.chinese: 我真沒了主意，不知如何才能付清這筆帳。

sentences.english: Inviter's payrolls and monthly bank statement in six months (Original).

sentences.chinese: 能，它還能處理任何帳目的存款和轉帳。

sentences.english: Du to bargain a yuan, chopped one yuan agreed to split firmly with him.

sentences.english: It discusses the reasons why the account beyond the law has existed, and how to prevent it.
sentences.chinese: 闡述了賬外帳存在的原因，並提出了預防措施。

sentences.english: The competent tax authorities shall strengthen their management on the business accounting of tax deduction ledgers .

sentences.english: Through her works, my favorite one is Xiamuyourenzhang.

sentences.english: They that reckon without their host are to reckon twice.
sentences.chinese: 店主不在便結帳，還得結第二次帳。

sentences.english: Direct post or transfer transaction to account receivable.

sentences.english: My dad has done his homework - he thinks we could have gained an extra 12 points!

sentences.english: Establish and register the accounts. Take care of statistic materials.

sentences.english: I was charged from March 10 till March 31.
